text: Iratxe García Pérez (; born 7 October 1974) is a Spanish politician. She is a member of the Spanish Socialist Workers' Party (PSOE). She has been a Member of the European Parliament since 2004. She also has been the Leader of the Progressive Alliance of Socialists and Democrats parliamentary group since 2019. ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:MEPs for Spain Category:Spanish socialists
